snippet.title: Best VGM 2411 - X-Men vs Street Fighter - Wolverine's Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 577 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2O4aNHy2Dcc

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / Playstation / Saturn
X-Men vs Street Fighter (1996)
Wolverine's Theme
Yuki Iwai & Yuko Kadota
